profile: At Steam Dry Canada, our customers are our business. services:
Air Duct Cleaning
Improve home’s air quality, provide allergy relief, and reduce the risk of home fires.

Furnace Cleaning
Improve energy efficiency from 10-47% and extend the useful life of your furnace.

Dryer Vent Cleaning
Prevent one of the most common causes of home fires.

Our camera-assisted ventilation inspections can identify problems and improve your home’s energy efficiency.

Heating and A/C Coil Cleaning
Cleaning dirty coils will make your air conditioning or heating system more efficient, lowering your utility bills.

Air Exchange System Cleaning
Keeping your air exchanger running efficiently helps protect the air in your home and family’s health.

Central Vacuum System Cleaning
Restore lost suction and improve your central vacuum system’s performance.

profile:
Serving Saskatoon and district, McIvor Power Vac Ltd. provides a thorough multi-step cleaning process, to help your family breathe easier. Cleaning your furnace ductwork will result in cleaner air and increased efficiency. We use state of the art equipment combined with knowledge, experience and integrity to do the job right.

The experts at McIvor Power Vac provide several services including duct cleaning, as well as cleaning: air conditioner coils, dryer vents, central vacs, hot water tanks and more. We recommend you clean your furnace and ducts during the furnace replacement process, after renovations or when new construction is complete.

McIvor Power Vac is referred by Saskatoon’s leading heating companies. For less dust for you and your family, call our team.

You can call us anytime at 306-222-3478 or email us at moc.gninaelctcudrovicm@ofni .

Call McIvor and breathe easier!
